  ,"privacyPolicyTitle":"Privacy Policy for Rubricator"
  ,"privacyPolicyLastUpdated":"Last updated: 19.04.2026"
  ,"privacyPolicySection1Title":"1. Introduction"
  ,"privacyPolicySection1Body1":"Welcome to Rubricator (\"we\", \"our\", or \"us\"). Rubricator is a social reading platform where users can discover books, create lists, track reading habits, and share content."
  ,"privacyPolicySection1Body2":"This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application."
  ,"privacyPolicySection2Title":"2. Information We Collect"
  ,"privacyPolicySection21Title":"2.1 Personal Information"
  ,"privacyPolicySection21Item1":"- Email address"
  ,"privacyPolicySection21Item2":"- Username"
  ,"privacyPolicySection21Item3":"- Profile information (optional)"
  ,"privacyPolicySection22Title":"2.2 User-Generated Content"
  ,"privacyPolicySection22Item1":"- Book reviews"
  ,"privacyPolicySection22Item2":"- Ratings"
  ,"privacyPolicySection22Item3":"- Quotes"
  ,"privacyPolicySection22Item4":"- Lists you create"
  ,"privacyPolicySection22Item5":"- Comments"
  ,"privacyPolicySection23Title":"2.3 Usage Data"
  ,"privacyPolicySection23Item1":"- App usage interactions"
  ,"privacyPolicySection23Item2":"- Feature usage (e.g., lists, stats, search)"
  ,"privacyPolicySection23Item3":"- Device information (OS version, device type)"
  ,"privacyPolicySection24Title":"2.4 Authentication Data"
  ,"privacyPolicySection24Item1":"- Basic profile information"
  ,"privacyPolicySection24Item2":"- Email address"
  ,"privacyPolicySection3Title":"3. How We Use Your Information"
  ,"privacyPolicySection3Item1":"- Provide and maintain the app"
  ,"privacyPolicySection3Item2":"- Enable social features (lists, comments, likes)"
  ,"privacyPolicySection3Item3":"- Personalize content and recommendations"
  ,"privacyPolicySection3Item4":"- Improve app performance and features"
  ,"privacyPolicySection3Item5":"- Communicate important updates"
  ,"privacyPolicySection4Title":"4. Data Storage and Security"
  ,"privacyPolicySection4Body":"Your data is stored securely using third-party infrastructure such as Supabase."
  ,"privacyPolicySection4Item1":"- Secure authentication"
  ,"privacyPolicySection4Item2":"- Encrypted connections (HTTPS)"
  ,"privacyPolicySection4Item3":"- Access control mechanisms"
  ,"privacyPolicySection5Title":"5. Data Sharing"
  ,"privacyPolicySection5Body":"We do NOT sell your personal data."
  ,"privacyPolicySection5Item1":"- With service providers (e.g., backend hosting)"
  ,"privacyPolicySection5Item2":"- To comply with legal obligations"
  ,"privacyPolicySection5Item3":"- To protect user safety and rights"
  ,"privacyPolicySection6Title":"6. Public Content"
  ,"privacyPolicySection6Item1":"- Public lists"
  ,"privacyPolicySection6Item2":"- Reviews"
  ,"privacyPolicySection6Item3":"- Comments"
  ,"privacyPolicySection6Body":"Content you share publicly may be visible to other users."
  ,"privacyPolicySection7Title":"7. Data Retention"
  ,"privacyPolicySection7Item1":"- As long as your account is active"
  ,"privacyPolicySection7Item2":"- Or as needed to provide services"
  ,"privacyPolicySection7Body":"You may request deletion of your data at any time."
  ,"privacyPolicySection8Title":"8. Your Rights"
  ,"privacyPolicySection8Item1":"- Access your data"
  ,"privacyPolicySection8Item2":"- Update your information"
  ,"privacyPolicySection8Item3":"- Request deletion of your account"
  ,"privacyPolicySection8Item4":"- Withdraw consent"
  ,"privacyPolicySection8Body":"To exercise these rights, contact us at:"
  ,"privacyPolicySection8Email":"Email: [YOUR EMAIL]"
  ,"privacyPolicySection9Title":"9. Children's Privacy"
  ,"privacyPolicySection9Body1":"Rubricator is not intended for users under the age of 13."
  ,"privacyPolicySection9Body2":"We do not knowingly collect data from children."
  ,"privacyPolicySection10Title":"10. Third-Party Services"
  ,"privacyPolicySection10Item1":"- Google (authentication, analytics)"
  ,"privacyPolicySection10Item2":"- Supabase (data storage)"
  ,"privacyPolicySection10Body":"These services have their own privacy policies."
  ,"privacyPolicySection11Title":"11. International Data Transfers"
  ,"privacyPolicySection11Body":"Your information may be processed in different countries where our service providers operate."
  ,"privacyPolicySection12Title":"12. Changes to This Privacy Policy"
  ,"privacyPolicySection12Body":"We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected by updating the \"Last updated\" date."
  ,"privacyPolicySection13Title":"13. Contact Us"
  ,"privacyPolicySection13Body":"If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us:"
  ,"privacyPolicySection13Email":"Email: ismailyucelolmez514@gmail.com"
  ,"privacyPolicyFooter":"By using Rubricator, you agree to this Privacy Policy."
